abstract: Ryan Moore takes third-round lead at Valspar Championship golf tournament; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Moore survived some errant shots early before reeling off four late birdies to take a one-stroke lead over Jordan Spieth after the third round at the Valspar Championship in Palm Harbor, Fla.

headline.main: Ryan Moore Recovers From a Shaky Start
headline.print_headline: Moore Recovers From a Shaky Start
